no.uib.cipr.matrix.io

Class MatrixInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.uib.cipr.matrix.io.MatrixInfo

  • public class MatrixInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains information on a matrix in the Matrix Market exchange format. Supports all valid matrices.
